        <p class="TableTextEmphasis">MadCap|slideshow</p>
        <p class="TableText">Modifies the look of the container holding the entire slideshow. Keep in mind that if you have competing styles set, those set in the MadCap|slide style take precedence. For example, if you set the background on MadCap|slideshow to blue and the background on MadCap|slide to yellow, the background will be yellow. But if you then change the background for MadCap|slide to (default), the background will show as blue.</p>
        <p class="TableText" MadCap:conditions="General.Online-Only">
            <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../Flare/Slideshows/Editing-Slideshow-Styles.htm">Editing Slideshow Styles</MadCap:xref>
        </p>
    </body>
